room_title: Escape room "The Puzzle Master's Room" by The Escape Artist KC in Kansas City
room_address: 408 B. East 18th St. Kansas City, MO 64108
room_description:
Are you ready to be challenged? The Puzzle Master would be happy to oblige! We can already hear him laughing. You'll need some serious brainpower to solve this one... It's frustratingly cool; mind-bendingly spectacular; intensely fun, and best of all... Lasers.
Enter the lair of the master! The crazy is evident. Can you bend your perspective enough to solve it?
